ll.yml — Spelling verification\n- [ ] Create `.github/workflows/codespell.yml`\n- [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n- [ ] Add backup/remove for `pyproject.toml`, `package.json`, `package-lock.json`\n- [ ] Add `pip install codespell`\n- [ ] Add `codespell` with `--check-filenames`, `--skip`, `--ignore-words-list`\n- [ ] Add restore step for backed-up files\n- [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/codespell.yml`\n\n### T009: copyright-check.yml — Copyright header enforcement\n- [ ] Create `.github/workflows/copyright-check.yml`\n- [ ] Configure `pull_request` trigger for `main`, `release-*`\n- [ ] Add `dorny/paths-filter@v2` with `copyright` filter (exclude `*.md`, `*.svg`, `*.png`, `docs/**`, `.github/**`)\n- [ ] Add `apt install moreutils` (for `ts` command)\n- [ ] Add `make gen-copyright` step\n- [ ] Add `git diff --exit-code` to verify no changes\n- [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/copyright-check.yml`\n\n---\n\n## Phase 5: Release Workflows\n\n### T010: build-push-release.yml — Release image publishing\n- [ ] Create `.github/workflows/build-push-release.yml`\n- [ ] Configure `push` trigger for `main` branch and tags `v*.*.*`, `v*.*.*-*`\n- [ ] Add `actions/checkout@v3` (older version as per spec)\n- [ ] Add `actions/setup-go@v4` with Go 1.24.4\n- [ ] Add `docker/setup-buildx-action@v2`\n- [ ] Add `docker/login-action@v3` for GHCR (`ghcr.io`)\n- [ ] Set `TAG` from git ref and `IMAGE_REGISTRY=ghcr.io/${{ github.repository_owner }}`\n- [ ] Add `make docker-buildx-push` (workload manager)\n- [ ] Add `make docker-buildx-push-router`\n- [ ] Add `make docker-buildx-push-picod`\n- [ ] Verify: `actionlint .github/workflows/build-push-release.yml`\n\n### T011: dify-plugin-publish.yml — Dify plugin release automation\n- [ ] Create `.github/workflows/dify-plugin-publish.yml`\n- [ ] Configure `push` trigger for tags `dify-plugin/v*`\n- [ ] Add download step for `dify-plugin` CLI 0.0.6\n- [ ] Add `yq` installation\n- [ ] Read and parse 